Overview
Technical
2, 3, and 4 point testing
Stakeless or clamp-on testing option
ART (Attached Rod Technique) capability
Multiple, user selectable test frequencies
Resistance measurement range to 200 kΩ
IP54 rated
Warning indicators prevent test failure
Simple one button operation
Included leads, stakes, calibration certificate, and rugged carry case
Optional
earth testing kit (ETK)
available
The DET4 contractor series of four-terminal digital earth/ground testers offers a comprehensive solution to your ground stake and soil resistivity testing needs. The series includes:
DET4TD2
: Dry-cell battery powered basic 4-terminal earth/ground tester
DET4TR2
: Rechargeable battery powered basic 4-terminal earth/ground tester
DET4TC2
: Dry-cell battery powered 4-terminal tester with selectable test frequencies, greater measurement sensitivity and attached rod technique (ART) and stakeless measurement capability
DET4TCR2
: Rechargeable battery powered 4-terminal earth/ground tester with selectable test frequencies, greater measurement sensitivity, ART, and stakeless measurement capability
The DET4TD, DET4TC and DET4TCR replace the DET5/4R and DET5/4D.
